content:
Valentine's Day is also the perfect occasion for dress-up: that's why all players can load up on Pink, Red, and White Weapon tints, and all Valentine's Day Massacre Special Clothing for free this week.

You can also pick up the Prohibition-era Gusenberg Sweeper free of charge from all participating Ammu-Nation locations citywide.
